# Practice

#### New examples of bias in AI technology are being uncovered frequently. Spend some time doing your own research for up-to-date information on bias in AI. You can do a general search or try to find examples specific to education or to your subject area.

## Educator’s Choice

#### Find and read at least one news article from a reputable source. You’ll reflect on what you read in the next level.

#### Bonus points if you use <a href="https://www.bing.com/chat" target="_blank">Copilot</a> to help you in your search!


